Steps for running Linux environment

  1. Clone the repository with the command git clone --branch es http://96.126.100.137:3000/auditoria_revision/Discovery.git Discovery
  2. When the repository has been cloned, go to the path of the repository and execute the command sudo npx vuepress dev
